Make sure to replace `'field_1234567890'` with the actual key of your ACF field. You can find the field key in the ACF field group settings.

3. Register ACF fields for custom post types: To expose ACF fields for custom post types, you need to modify the above code slightly. Replace `'page'` with the slug of your custom post type in the `register_rest_field` function. For example, if your custom post type slug is `'book'`, the code will look like this:

