    public function __construct()
    {
        $this->closure = function () {
            // ...
        };
    }

    // ...
}
```

You should refactor it to remove the closure:

```php
class MyJob implements ShouldQueue
{
    protected $data;

    public function __construct($data)
    {
        $this->data = $data;
    }

